{"article_id":"q0aEEw6LeIX2Wmxb","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"House Republican leaders Thursday pushed for a short-term bill","depth":8},{"id":1,"text":"to fund Homeland Security","depth":9},{"id":2,"text":"and avoid a department shutdown this weekend ,","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"hoping to buy more time","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"to force Senate Democrats into negotiations over President Obama ' s deportation amnesty .","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"House Speaker John A. Boehner presented the plan to his conference at a closed-door meeting ,","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"arguing","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"that keeping the Homeland Security Department open with a three-week funding bill would strengthen Republicans ' bargaining position ,","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"according to lawmakers in attendance .","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"The extra time ,","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"he said ,","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"would be used","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"to cajole Senate Democrats to follow the legislative process and enter into a conference committee","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"to reconcile the House-passed bill ,","depth":12},{"id":14,"text":"which included measures","depth":13},{"id":15,"text":"to block Mr. Obama ' s immigration actions ,","depth":13},{"id":16,"text":"and the Senate ' s expected \" clean \" bill","depth":12},{"id":17,"text":"that will fund Homeland Security without changes .","depth":12},{"id":18,"text":"The Senate will vote on that bill Friday morning ,","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"but Minority Leader Harry Reid has vowed not to allow a conference committee ,","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"suggesting","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"the stalemate will continue .","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"\" We are not going to be part of their petty games , \"","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"said the Nevada Democrat .","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"The House , meanwhile , will vote on its short-term bill Friday","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"- though conservative lawmakers were skeptical of Mr. Boehner ' s plan ,","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"which depends on cooperation from Democrats .","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"\" Time will tell","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"if we are in a different position","depth":12},{"id":29,"text":"[ in three weeks ]","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"then we are now","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"and how much strength the speaker has then , \"","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"said Rep. Walter P. Jones , North Carolina Republican .","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"\" We cave in all the time up here . \"","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"The strategy emerged","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"just hours after Mr. Boehner , Ohio Republican , took his most aggressive stance yet in the standoff .","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"\" It is outrageous that Senate Democrats are using Homeland Security funding for blackmail","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"to protect the actions of the president ,","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"when the president himself said","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"he didn ' t have the authority","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"to do this , \"","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"Mr. Boehner said at his weekly press conference .","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"The speaker is under intense pressure from Democrats to relent ,","depth":5},{"id":43,"text":"and from a large faction of his conference to hang tough against Mr. Obama ' s actions ,","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"which seek to grant legal status , work permits and Social Security numbers to more than 4 million illegal immigrants .","depth":6},{"id":45,"text":"He repeatedly noted the 22 times","depth":6},{"id":46,"text":"that Mr. Obama claimed","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"that he did not have the authority","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"to change immigration law","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"before he took the action in November , a move","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"Mr. Boehner and other Republicans call lawless","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"regardless of the substantive merits .","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"\" The Congress of the United States can not look the other way","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"and act","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"like it didn ' t happen , \"","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"said Mr. Boehner .","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"\" The courts aren ' t looking the other way .","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"This is a violation of our Constitution .","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"It ' s a violation of the balance of powers in our Constitution","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"and it needs to be addressed","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"and we ' re doing it . \"","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"Several Republican lawmakers have insisted","depth":6},{"id":62,"text":"that the shutdown is a bluff by Democrats ,","depth":6},{"id":63,"text":"because nearly 90 percent of the department ' s employees are deemed \" essential personnel \"","depth":6},{"id":64,"text":"who would work during a shutdown","depth":7},{"id":65,"text":"and eventually get paid .","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"Still , Democrats and some Republicans remain convinced","depth":5},{"id":67,"text":"that the GOP will get blamed for any government shutdown .","depth":5},{"id":68,"text":"Mr. Reid tried to use the terrorist threat","depth":5},{"id":69,"text":"to ratchet up the pressure ,","depth":5},{"id":70,"text":"demanding the House pass a \" clean \" funding bill","depth":6},{"id":71,"text":"without measures","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"to block the president ' s immigration actions .","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"\" The American people are frightened ,","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"and rightfully so .","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"ISIS appears to have money ,","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"terrorists appear to have money ,","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"why shouldn ' t our homeland have the ability","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"to protect itself , \"","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"he said earlier at the Capitol .","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"\" This is like living in a world of crazy people . \"","depth":6},{"id":81,"text":"Senate Democrats on Wednesday ended the filibuster","depth":4},{"id":82,"text":"they sustained for most of February ,","depth":4},{"id":83,"text":"allowing the House-passed bill to advance","depth":4},{"id":84,"text":"after Senate Majority Leader Mitch McConnell , Kentucky Republican , agreed to strip out the anti-amnesty provisions .","depth":4},{"id":85,"text":"The deal included a vote on separate legislation against Mr. Obama ' s actions ,","depth":3},{"id":86,"text":"but that would come later .","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":173,"left":167,"right":172,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":167,"left":147,"right":166,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":147,"left":128,"right":146,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":128,"left":110,"right":127,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":110,"left":104,"right":109,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":104,"left":91,"right":103,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":91,"left":89,"right":90,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":89,"left":0,"right":88,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":88,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":90,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":103,"left":94,"right":102,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":94,"left":5,"right":93,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":93,"left":92,"right":8,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":92,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":102,"left":95,"right":101,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":95,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":101,"left":11,"right":100,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":100,"left":12,"right":99,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":99,"left":97,"right":98,"relation":"same-unit","